thread.title: Zhane Pritchard
thread.title_full: Paper Divas reviewed by Zhane Pritchard

author: Zhane Pritchard
title: Zhane Pritchard
text: I loved Paper Divas, had invitations for everything I needed and at a cheap price. The service was amazing, received my order within 2 days and the packaging it came in was great protection for the invites. Would highly recommend paper divas to anyone and use it again.
